# Changelog

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.9] - 2026-04-28

- Made `geodepot get` print only the resolved case path on stdout, so it can be used directly in scripts.
- Improved packaging/runtime handling by bundling GDAL and PROJ data correctly and keeping compiled executables intact.
- Fixed the first-time Pixi configuration setup and clarified the related user-facing docs.

## [1.0.8] - 2026-04-22

- Fixed the Linux installer tag lookup to avoid the `curl: (23)` broken-pipe failure.
- Added installer progress output for POSIX and Windows installs.
- Made `geodepot init` work without requiring the GDAL/OGR runtime at import time.
- Added a CI audit that rejects bundles with unresolved native dependencies or build-path leakage.
- Updated the Unix launcher to export the bundled native library path before starting Geodepot.

## [1.0.7] - 2026-04-01

## [1.0.6] - 2026-04-01

## [1.0.5] - 2026-04-01

- Switched release packaging to Pixi-based bundles instead of PyInstaller.
- Added top-level launcher wrappers that activate the bundled runtime before starting `geodepot`.
- Added POSIX and PowerShell installer scripts for downloading and installing release bundles.
- Updated the user-facing install and release docs for the new bundle layout and installer flow.
- Consolidated developer recipes around Pixi and `just`, and removed the old PyInstaller experiment files.

## [1.0.0] - TBD

First release.
